    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>寻找 Eddie Velvet。</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >私家侦探 Red Walker 来到了半荒废、半遗忘的偏远小镇银松镇，只为追查 Eddie Velvet 的下落。Velvet 是一位失踪的音乐家。随着案件逐渐揭开一段黑暗的过往，Walker 很快便陷入了一种诡异且如噩梦般的失控坠落状态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333000/extras/b1c89dbaf7d913f3e848a802765f22e2.avif?t=1771590268\" width=780 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上一段恐惧氛围十足的旅程。被往昔阴影所困扰的银松镇正等待着揭开它黑暗的秘密。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333000/extras/1a53b9325826688be5c1532228fc3465.poster.avif?t=1771590268\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333000/extras/1a53b9325826688be5c1532228fc3465.webm?t=1771590268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333000/extras/1a53b9325826688be5c1532228fc3465.mp4?t=1771590268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">***</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333000/extras/f9c5e5521be23bd0b1c3499079cdfd63.avif?t=1771590268\" width=780 height=110 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一封致敬经典生存恐怖游戏的情书。在搜刮资源、破解阻挡去路的谜题时，你必须直面或躲避小镇中的种种恐怖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333000/extras/7dd659f54fbcc1bd831251f0e3683a24.poster.avif?t=1771590268\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333000/extras/7dd659f54fbcc1bd831251f0e3683a24.webm?t=1771590268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333000/extras/7dd659f54fbcc1bd831251f0e3683a24.mp4?t=1771590268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">***</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333000/extras/8aff68b6b10f599acdfa1a926aea18ef.avif?t=1771590268\" width=780 height=110 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >紧锁的门扉与隐秘的路径无处不在，每一次转弯都可能揭开未被发现的线索、资源或是黑暗中蛰伏的未知事物。随着更精良的工具和武器逐渐解锁，小镇中越来越多的区域将变得可探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333000/extras/542db35391351bdac12b5f8fb4c2eb1c.poster.avif?t=1771590268\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333000/extras/542db35391351bdac12b5f8fb4c2eb1c.webm?t=1771590268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333000/extras/542db35391351bdac12b5f8fb4c2eb1c.mp4?t=1771590268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">***</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333000/extras/4e3c49d8799e0f8b7b0e3a8ec4118a9f.avif?t=1771590268\" width=780 height=110 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这座城镇的恐怖之处在于，这里栖息着种类繁多的强悍怪物与魁梧首领，每场遭遇战都充满紧张与危险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333000/extras/d73cc8971d663138d581f528d2f75c5e.poster.avif?t=1771590268\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333000/extras/d73cc8971d663138d581f528d2f75c5e.webm?t=1771590268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333000/extras/d73cc8971d663138d581f528d2f75c5e.mp4?t=1771590268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">***</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333000/extras/e7ec9265dd5cbacdc71b1b14b115bf92.avif?t=1771590268\" width=780 height=110 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >物品栏的空间有限。尽可能地寻找物品吧，每颗子弹、每瓶药品和每次升级都至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333000/extras/87068e7711486141cb266d8a237818e0.poster.avif?t=1771590268\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333000/extras/87068e7711486141cb266d8a237818e0.webm?t=1771590268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333000/extras/87068e7711486141cb266d8a237818e0.mp4?t=1771590268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
